                    Filter Cond: (include_rounds_main.category = 20)  𝄀
                    Runtime Filter Probe: include_rounds_main.id  𝄀
              ->  Join  𝄀
                    Join Type: INNER  𝄀
                    Join Cond: (mo_ivf_alias_0.pkid = include_rounds_main.id)  𝄀
                    Runtime Filter Build: #[10,0]  𝄀
